  "texts": [
    "In conclusion, while S ide.1 successfully extracts keywords that accurately reflect the needs, there are extraction failures in handling colloquial content.",
    "This highlights the need for improvement in accuracy, particularly with a focus on preventing extraction failures.",
    "Fig. 16 Graph of ExperimentRegarding RQ3, we discuss the results of Experiment 3, which evaluates case retrieval.",
    "From the median of the box plot in Fig. 16 and the Hit Rate A in Table 2, it is evident that both S ide.1 and S col.1 found at least one case in more than half of the searches.",
    "Additionally, Fig. 17 shows that when at least one case was found, multiple cases were often retrieved."
  ]
